prompts.prompt:
Generate a Spring Boot REST controller for the resource {{ResourceName}}. Include:
- @RestController and @RequestMapping annotations
- GET /{{resource}} with optional pagination
- GET /{{resource}}/{id}
- POST with @Valid @RequestBody
- PUT /{{resource}}/{id}
- DELETE /{{resource}}/{id}
- Proper HTTP status codes (200, 201, 204, 404)
- Constructor-injected service
- Javadoc for each endpoint
